Key Match Events: Bafana thrashed Congo Brazzaville 5-0 with goals from Bathusi Aubaas, Lyle Foster, Iqraam Rayners, and a brace by Teboho Mokoena
Pre-Game Insights: Bafana coach Hugo Broos voiced out his concern about the synthetic pitch at Stade Alphonse Massamba-Debat de Brazzavile
Bafana will look for nothing but a victory to book their ticket to Morocco next year
Miscellaneous Highlights: The match will take place at the Stade Alphonse Massamba-Debat de Brazzavile with a synthetic pitch
